data.description:
Wonderful, lakefront home in gated, resort style community of Palm Beach Plantation located within an excellent, Wellington school zone. Come inside and be wowed by the open concept layout, spacious living areas and beautiful flooring throughout along with an inviting kitchen. All of the bedrooms are spacious as well. Outside you will enjoy a lovely backyard overlooking the serene lake. Live the resort life style in Palm Beach Plantation a meticulously maintained community with a lovely recreational facility which offers its residents a pool, state of the art fitness center, clubhouse and much more! Conveniently located just minutes from I-95, the Turnpike, Palm Beach International Airport and world renowned Wellington this home is a MUST see!

Looking to sell a home or want a quick home valuation www.HomeValuePalmBeach.com. For more information on this home please call Jeff Tricoli at  561-220-9208, email info@tricoliteam.com or visit: www.TricoliTeam.com
